{"id":587172,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【众人推】《this-is-the-china-xi》/","date":"2018-06-19T06:23:00Z","modified":"2018-06-19T08:10:35Z","title":"【众人推】《This is the China Xi》","content":"<p>6月18日，有推特网友转发了一首讽刺习近平（Uncle Xi）的改编曲，这首改编的歌曲来自6月17日HBO脱口秀节目《Xi Jinping: Last Week Tonight with John Oliver》。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">唱支山歌给党听😄 <a href=\"https://t.co/khpHiVkRBF\">pic.twitter.com/khpHiVkRBF</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Super Mario (@SuperMa22042567) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SuperMa22042567/status/1008637328116482049?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 18, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>原歌曲《The Belt and Road is How》由新华社海外版New China TV发布于2017年5月。歌曲借助小孩之口为一带一路唱赞歌，改编版则辛辣讽刺了“习大大”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/官媒.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587180\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/官媒.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"174\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/官媒.jpg 988w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/官媒-300x95.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/官媒-768x243.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M0lJc3PMNIg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>在《Xi Jinping: Last Week Tonight with John Oliver》节目的19分11秒出现了这首改编的歌曲《This is the China Xi》（网友起名）</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k8wtKadWIfA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>Xi Jinping: Last Week Tonight with John Oliver (HBO) 完整节目：</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OubM8bD9kck?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>6月19日，有推特网友开始进行“接力翻译”，并制作了该歌曲的<strong>中文字幕版本：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">大外宣被John oliver加工一下，瞬间观看量过三万（通常在1k以下）一带一路在世界人民面前露脸了<a href=\"https://t.co/ML6BQu94UX\">https://t.co/ML6BQu94UX</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; China’s New-Gen Civil Force (CNCF) (@fb_china_today) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/fb_china_today/status/1008825096604127233?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 18, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">加字幕，接力吴三桂&#8230; <a href=\"https://t.co/ZCMKn8eB0B\">pic.twitter.com/ZCMKn8eB0B</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 方觉 (@InFangjay) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/InFangjay/status/1008912586216235008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 19, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p>中国数字空间｜<a title=\"习近平个人崇拜\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\">习近平个人崇拜</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[34970,34969,27070,13222,29740]}